quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Tha Sin Mim Tuhan nyang teupeue meukeusud ayat Sabab Hadharat hana Neupeugah
  26,2,Nyoekeuh dum ayat di dalam kitab Qur’an nyoe meuhat cit trang sileupah
  26,3,Sang-sang digata gadoh seumangat Watee taingat jipeubuet salah Pakon jih batat han jimeuiman
  26,4,Sabe sit meunan dum kaphe jadah Meu Kamoe kheundak Meupeutron ayat Saboh muʻjizat nyang hebat leupah Sideh di langet Meupeutron ayat Mangat jih teupat jiteukui bagah
  26,5,Beurangpeue ayat teuka lom bak jih Teutap sit dijih hana jipapah Ayat nyang baro teuka bak Tuhan Han jipeureumeun jipaleng bagah
  26,6,Ka jikheun sulet han jitem pateh Dudoe bak droejih teuma geupeugah Bandum geubalah teuma nyan dijih Nyang jipeu-eleh jikheun beurakah
  26,7,Peue hana jieu di dalam bumoe Bak kayee sinoe hijo dum indah Kamoe peuudep dumna tanaman Meupasang-pasang galakteuh leupah
  26,8,Bandum atra nyan sit jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Maha Peumurah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Dijih bandum nyan hana phaedah
  26,9,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,10,Watee Neumeuhei uleh Po gata b4 Tajak hai Musa keudeh talangkah 4 Kaom nyang lalem kaphe keu Tuhan
  26,11,Kaom Peuraʻeun nyang that seurakah Pakon bandum jih han jitakwa
  26,12,Geukheun le Musa wahe ya Allah Lon takot sulet jipeugah keu lon Han jipateh lon jikheun beurakah
  26,13,Seumpet dada lon han glah lidah lon Neukirem Harun lom Neuyue peugah
  26,14,Dilon na salah pih bak awak nyan Takot jipoh lon jimeung tueng balah
  26,15,Neukheun hana peue tajak bandua Ò Kamoe bri tanda nyang raya tuah Kamoe Meudeungo peue-peue nyang jikheun
  26,16,Ubak Peuraʻeun keudeh tapeugah Kamoe nyoe Rasul Tuhan Po alam
  26,17,Awak kamoe nyan Neuyue peuleupah Bani Israil tajok keu kamoe
  26,18,Jiseuot meunoe laju jipeugah Kon gata dilee kamoe peulahra Yoh mantong gata si manyak mirah Padum thon sabe taduek ngon kamoe
  26,19,Tapeubuet dudoe buet nyang that salah oi Dum guna kamoe hana tapike Tatem jak kaphe hana tapeugah
  26,20,Geukheun buet lon nyan sabab meularat Watee nyan sisat lon ka roh salah
  26,21,Nyankeuh jeuet lon plueng keudeh u lua Takot keu gata tameung tueng balah Teuma di sideh Tuhan bri keu lon Hikmah keu lon Neubri got leupah Neupeujeuet treuk lon keu Rasul Tuhan
  26,22,Teuma nikmat nyan nyang gata peugah Tapeulahra lon yoh mantong ubit Ka tapeunamiet dum hamba Allah Bani Israil dum tapeunamiet Lalem that keubit elanya leupah
  26,23,Peuraʻeun tanyong boh nyang toh Tuhan Nyang Po dum alam bunoe tapeugah
  26,24,Geukheun Tuhan Po langet ngon bumoe Ngon bandum asoe bandum blah bicah Meu tatem pateh nyankeuh nyang Tuhan
  26,25,Peuraʻeun jikheun bak ngon jih bagah Nyan na tadeungo roe gata bandum
  26,26,Musa kheun Tuhan kuasa leupah Tuhan gata dum ngon yah-yah gata Nyang dilee masa dum ka beh leupah
  26,27,Jikheun Rasul nyan nyang jak bak gata Jih nyan ka gila akai ka ubah
  26,28,Geukheun Tuhan Po timu ngon barat Bandum lat batat peuneujeuet Allah Meunyo tapike ngon akai nyang got
  26,29,Jikheun bek le that haba tapeugah Meu takheun tuhan laen nibak lon Gata lam palong keudeh kukeubah Dalam glap seupot kupasoe gata
  26,30,Teuma kheun Musa deungo lon peugah Meunyo ek lon bri dali nyang nyata Teuma peue gata tatem meunyeurah
  26,31,Jikheun jok keunoe dali bak gata Meunyo bit beuna lagee tapeugah
  26,32,Geutiek treuk tungkat ka jeuet keu naga Uleue be raya nyata that leupah
  26,33,Geusuet ngon jaroe puteh meukeuprak Soe nyang ngieng rusak mata jih mirah
  26,34,Jikheun treuk laju bak rakan lingka Nyoe sihe raya carong jih leupah
  26,35,Jimeung peuteubiet gata lam nanggroe Teuh ngon sihe nyoe gata jirajah Boh peue tapeugot teuma keu jih nyoe
  26,36,Tayue preh jih nyoe teuma jipeugah Í Ngon aduen jih nyan tayue preh siat Ditanyoe rakyat jinoe dum takrah Ban saboh nanggroe meusapat keunoe
  26,37,Sihe geutanyoe pih carong leupah d Sihe nyang utoh bandum tayue jak
  26,38,Bandum treuk jijak keunan dum bagah Bak watee uroe nyang ka jimaklum
  26,39,Jitanyong bandum ka troh talangkah
  26,40,Mangat taikot bandum sihe nyan Meunyo ek meunang lagee jipeugah
  26,41,‘Ohban troh keunan dum tukang sihe Ka jitanyong le jilakee upah Jilakee upah ubak Peuraʻeun Meu kamoe meunang peue na hadiah
  26,42,Jikheun hadiah cit na keu gata Gata ngon raja lom toe that leupah
  26,43,Geukheun le Musa boh tiek peue nyang na Nyang keunoe taba ‘oh Iheueh tarajah
  26,44,Jitiek treuk taloe ngon tungkat jih dum Deumi Peuraʻeun raja nyang meugah Geutanyoe meunang meunan dum jikheun
  26,45,Geutiek treuk keunan tungkat meutuah ‘Ohban ka geutiek tungkat le Musa Jiʻuet treuk sigra peue nyang meurimbah Abeh dum jiʻuet sihe awak nyan
  26,46,Teukeujet yoh nyan tukang meurajah Si tukang sihe bandum jisujud Í Sabab teukeujet jikalon ulah
  26,47,Jikheun treuk bandum kamoe meuiman Tuhan Po alam kuasa leupah
  26,48,Tuhan Po Musa ngon Tuhan Harun
  26,49,Beungeh Peuraʻeun jikheun treuk bagah Peue kameuiman laju keu jih nyan Gohlom kuizin le lon dum keu kah i Keubit gureekah jih nyang raya that Sihe dum meuhat jipeurunoe kah Nyoe beu kateupeue hukoman kubri Jaroe ngon gaki kukoh kutarah Jaroe ngon gaki kusurang sareng Lheueh nyan kupateng beu manyang leupah Bandum kuteupang u ateuh sula Nak bek biasa lawan peurintah
  26,50,Seuot awak nyan hana meularat Kamoe dum meuhat meuwoe bak Allah Ubak Po kamoe keudeh dum muewoe
  26,51,Neuampon kamoe meulakee bagah Raya that deecha kamoe baroekon Kamoe meuiman jinoe ya Allah Nyoekeuh dum kamoe nyang phon meuiman